properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const loSplit = thisLayer.effect('Lowly Worm')('Lower Split');if (loSplit == 100) {createPath([[0,0]], inTangents = [], outTangents = [], false)		} else {const baseWidth = thisLayer.effect('Lowly Worm')('Width') * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0] * 0.5;const myPath = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base').content('Path').path;const t = clamp(		thisLayer.effect('Lowly Worm')('Lower Split') * 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999		);const normalHere = myPath.normalOnPath(t);const pointHere = myPath.pointOnPath(t);createPath([sub(sub(pointHere, mul(normalHere, baseWidth)), normalHere), add(add(pointHere, mul(normalHere, baseWidth)), normalHere)], inTangents = [], outTangents = [], false)	}

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: const upSplit = thisLayer.effect('Lowly Worm')('Upper Split');const loSplit = thisLayer.effect('Lowly Worm')('Lower Split');if (loSplit < upSplit || upSplit == 0) {createPath([[0,0]], inTangents = [], outTangents = [], false)		} else {const baseWidth = thisLayer.effect('Lowly Worm')('Width') * thisLayer.content('Admin').content('Scaling Factors').transform.scale[0] * 0.5;const myPath = thisLayer.content('Limb').content('Base').content('Path').path;const t = clamp(		upSplit * 0.01, 0.0001, 0.999		);const normalHere = myPath.normalOnPath(t);const pointHere = myPath.pointOnPath(t);createPath([sub(sub(pointHere, mul(normalHere, baseWidth)), normalHere), add(add(pointHere, mul(normalHere, baseWidth)), normalHere)], inTangents = [], outTangents = [], false)}

properties.name: Path
properties.expression: function limbPath() {        // Limber Path Limb        const thisProp = thisProperty;        const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');        const curveLin = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('curvature').value[1] * 0.01;        if (curveLin === 0) {            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [], [], false);        }        else {            const inTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('inTangPos').value;            const outTangPos = endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('outTangPos').value;            return createPath([                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p0').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p1ikfkfreek').value,                endctrl('ADBE Effect Parade')('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('p2ikfkfreek').value,            ], [[0, 0], inTangPos, [0, 0]], [[0, 0], mul(outTangPos, -1), [0, 0]], false);        }    }limbPath();// Limber Library limbPath

properties.name: Scale
properties.expression: const endctrl = thisComp.layer('{{ end }}');const scaleFactor = endctrl.effect('Pseudo/skl_main_data_01')('scaleFactor').value[0];const widthScale = endctrl.effect('Limber')('Width Scale') * 0.01;[scaleFactor * widthScale, 0]
